This is a repository to hold code and datafiles relevant to the paper:
"Size-dependent lattice symmetry breaking determines the exciton fine 
structure of perovskite nanocrystals"


Contents:

	src - C source codes for the electronic structure calculations

	NC_structures - details and scripts for structural minimization

	graphics - scripts for generating the graphics in the paper

	electronic - input files and data from the electronic calculations 
				 for the cubic, orthorhombic and relaxed structures. See
				 the "example" sub-directory for annotated input scripts.

